- Sir! No. sir!

60
00:04:16.500 --> 00:04:19.500
Okay. Hey. thank you. At ease.

61
00:04:22.200 --> 00:04:24.700
Right here. Woody.
I'm red this time.

62
00:04:24.700 --> 00:04:28.600
- No. S-Slink-
- Oh. well. all right.
You can be red if you want.

63
00:04:28.500 --> 00:04:31.000
