76
00:05:08.900 --> 00:05:11.200
I was close to being scared that time.

77
00:05:11.200 --> 00:05:14.500
I'm going for fearsome here.
but I just don't feel it.

78
00:05:14.500 --> 00:05:16.800
I think I'm just
coming off as annoying.

79
00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:19.900
Owl Oh. hi. Bo. Hi.

80
00:05:19.900 --> 00:05:22.900
I wanted to thank you. Woody.
for saving my flock.

81
00:05:22.800 --> 00:05:25.200
Oh. hey.
it was. uh. nothin'.

82
00:05:25.200 --> 00:05:30.400
What do you say I get someone else
