83
00:05:30.300 --> 00:05:32.900
Oh. yeah!

84
00:05:32.900 --> 00:05:36.900
Remember. I'm just
a couple of blocks away.

85
00:05:36.900 --> 00:05:40.100
- Yodel-ay-hee-hoo!
- Come on. come on.
Smaller toys up front.

86
00:05:41.800 --> 00:05:43.700
Hey. Woody. come on.

87
00:05:46.600 --> 00:05:48.400
- Ahem!

88
00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:50.900
- Oh. thanks. Mike.

89
00:05:50.900 --> 00:05:53.600
- Okay- Whoa. whoa. Step back.

90
00:05:53.600 --> 00:05:56.000
- For crying out loud.
- Thank you.

91
00:05:56.000 --> 00:05:59.000
