That better? Great.

92
00:05:59.000 --> 00:06:02.800
Everybody hear me? Up on the shelf.
can you hear me? Great.

93
00:06:02.700 --> 00:06:05.900
Okay. First item today:

94
00:06:05.900 --> 00:06:09.200
Uh... oh. yeah.
Has everyone picked a moving buddy?

95
00:06:09.100 --> 00:06:11.800
- What?
- Moving buddy? You can't be serious.

96
00:06:11.800 --> 00:06:13.900
I didn't know we were
supposed to have one already.

97
00:06:13.900 --> 00:06:16.300
