98
00:06:16.300 --> 00:06:18.700
You guys think
this is a big joke.

99
00:06:18.700 --> 00:06:21.100
We've only got one week
left before the move.

100
00:06:21.100 --> 00:06:23.600
I don't want any toys left behind.
A moving buddy.

101
00:06:23.600 --> 00:06:26.300
If you don't have one.
get one!

102
00:06:26.300 --> 00:06:29.400
All right. next.
Uh. oh. yes.

103
00:06:29.400 --> 00:06:32.600
Tuesday night's plastic corrosion
awareness meeting...

104
00:06:32.500 --> 00:06:34.900
was. I think.
a big success.

105
00:06:34.900 --> 00:06:37.900
And we wanna thank Mr. Spell
for putting that on for us.

106
00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:40.700
