- You're welcome.

107
00:06:40.700 --> 00:06:44.000
Okay. Uh. oh. yes.
One. uh. minor note here.

108
00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:47.000
Andy's birthday party
has been moved to today.

109
00:06:46.900 --> 00:06:49.100
