110
00:06:49.100 --> 00:06:51.400
What do you mean the party's today?
His birthday's not till next week!

111
00:06:51.400 --> 00:06:54.000
What's goin' on down there?
Is his mom losin' her marbles?

112
00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:57.700
Well. obviously she wanted to
have the party before the move.

113
00:06:57.700 --> 00:07:00.900
- I'm not worried.
You shouldn't be worried.
- Of course Woody ain't worried.

114
00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:03.000
He's been Andy's favorite
since kindergarten.

115
00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:05.100
Hey. hey.
Come on. Potato Head.

116
00:07:05.200 --> 00:07:08.600
