a recon post downstairs. Code Red!

143
00:08:31.400 --> 00:08:33.900
- You know what to do.
- Yes. sir!

144
00:08:33.900 --> 00:08:36.400
All right. men.
You heard him. Code Red!

145
00:08:36.400 --> 00:08:39.600
Repeat. we are at Code Red.
Recon plan Charlie. Execute!

146
00:08:39.500 --> 00:08:41.500
Let's move!
Move. move. move. move!

147
00:08:59.600 --> 00:09:02.100
- Yeah!

148
00:09:02.100 --> 00:09:04.900
- Okay. come on. kids.

149
00:09:04.800 --> 00:09:07.700
Everyone in the living room.
It's almost time for the presents.

150
00:09:28.400 --> 00:09:30.700
All right. gangway. gangway.

151
00:09:30.700 --> 00:09:33.800
And this is
how we find out...

152
00:09:33.800 --> 00:09:36.000
- what is in those presents.

153
00:09:39.600 --> 00:09:42.500
Okay. who's hungry?

154
00:09:43.500 --> 00:09:45.300
Here come the chips!

155
00:09:45.300 --> 00:09:47.600
I've got Cool Ranch
and barbecue! Ow!

156
00:09:47.700 --> 00:09:49.700
What in the world-- Oh!

157
00:09:49.700 --> 00:09:52.500
