158
00:09:52.500 --> 00:09:55.500
Shouldn't they be there by now?
What's taking them so long?

159
00:09:55.600 --> 00:09:58.600
Hey. these guys are professionals.
They're the best.

160
00:09:58.500 --> 00:10:00.900
Come on!
They're not lying down on the job.

161
00:10:11.400 --> 00:10:13.600
G-G-Go on without me!
J-Just go!

162
00:10:13.600 --> 00:10:16.500
A good soldier never
leaves a man behind.

163
00:10:33.100 --> 00:10:35.300
- Okay. everybody. come on.

164
00:10:35.300 --> 00:10:38.300
Everybody settle down.
Now. kids. Everybody-

165
00:10:38.300 --> 00:10:42.200
You sit in a circle. No. Andy.
Andy. you sit in the middle there.

166
00:10:42.100 --> 00:10:46.300
- Good. And- Which present
are you gonna open first?

167
00:10:46.200 --> 00:10:49.000
- Mine!
- There they are.

168
00:10:49.000 --> 00:10:52.000
Come in.
Mother Bird. This is Alpha Bravo.

169
00:10:52.000 --> 00:10:54.600
- This is it! This is it!
Quiet. quiet. quiet!
- Come in. Mother Bird.

170
00:10:54.700 --> 00:10:57.500
Andy's opening the first present now.

171
00:10:57.400 --> 00:11:00.100
Mrs. Potato Head! Mrs. Potato Head!
Mrs. Potato Head!

172
00:11:00.100 --> 00:11:02.000
Hey. I can dream.
can't I?

173
00:11:02.000 --> 00:11:05.100
The bow's coming off.
He's ripping the wrapping paper.

174
00:11:05.100 --> 00:11:07.400
It's a- It's-
It's a- a lunch box.

175
00:11:07.400 --> 00:11:09.500
- We've got a lunch box here.
- A lunch box?

176
00:11:09.500 --> 00:11:11.400
- Lunch box?
- For lunch.

177
00:11:11.400 --> 00:11:13.600
Okay. second present.
It appears to be--

178
00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:16.500
- Okay. it's bed sheets.
- Who invited that kid?

179
00:11:21.400 --> 00:11:23.800
Oh! Only one left.

180
00:11:23.800 --> 00:11:26.200
- Okay. we're on the last present now.
- Last present!

181
00:11:26.200 --> 00:11:28.500
It's a big one.
It's a--

182
00:11:28.500 --> 00:11:30.800
- It's a board game!
Repeat. Battleship!
- Whew!

183
00:11:30.800 --> 00:11:33.000
- Hallelujah!

184
00:11:33.000 --> 00:11:34.900
- Yeah! All right!
- Hey. watch it!

185
00:11:34.900 --> 00:11:36.800
Sorry there.
old spud head.

186
00:11:36.800 --> 00:11:40.500
Mission accomplished. Well done. men.
Pack it up. We're goin' home.

187
00:11:40.500 --> 00:11:43.000
So did I tell ya?
Huh? Nothin' to worry about.

188
00:11:43.000 --> 00:11:46.300
I knew you were right all along. Woody.
Never doubted ya for a second.

189
00:11:46.200 --> 00:11:49.100
Wait a minute. Oh!

190
00:11:49.100 --> 00:11:52.600
- What do we have here?
- Wait! Turn that thing back on!

191
00:11:52.600 --> 00:11:55.100
Come in. Mother Bird!
Come in. Mother Bird!

192
00:11:55.100 --> 00:11:57.200
Mom has pulled a surprise
present from the closet.

193
00:11:57.200 --> 00:11:59.800
Andy's opening it.
He's really excited about this one.

194
00:11:59.800 --> 00:12:02.200
- Mom. what is it?
- It's a huge package.

195
00:12:02.200 --> 00:12:04.900
Oh. get outta the-- One of the kids
is in the way. I can't see.

196
00:12:04.900 --> 00:12:08.000
- It's a--
- Wow!

197
00:12:07.900 --> 00:12:12.200
- It's a what? What is it?

198
00:12:12.100 --> 00:12:14.600
- Oh. no!
- Oh. ya big lizard!

199
00:12:14.600 --> 00:12:17.400
