- Way to go. Rex!

200
00:12:17.400 --> 00:12:19.900
- No. no! Turn him around!
Turn him around!
- He's puttin' 'em in backwa-

201
00:12:19.900 --> 00:12:21.800
Here. you're
puttin' 'em in backwards!

202
00:12:21.800 --> 00:12:25.400
Plus is positive. minus is negative!
Oh. let me!

203
00:12:25.400 --> 00:12:27.900
- Let's go to my room. guys!

204
00:12:27.900 --> 00:12:30.400
Red alert! Red alert!
Andy is coming upstairs!

205
00:12:30.400 --> 00:12:32.900
- There!
- Juvenile intrusion!

206
00:12:32.900 --> 00:12:34.800
Repeat. resume
your positions now!

207
00:12:34.800 --> 00:12:36.700
Andy's coming! Everybody.
back to your places! Hurry!

208
00:12:36.700 --> 00:12:38.600
Get to your places!
Get to your places!

209
00:12:38.600 --> 00:12:41.200
- Where's my ear? Who's seen my ear?
Did you see my ear?

210
00:12:41.200 --> 00:12:45.000
Out of my way! Here I come!
Here I come!

211
00:12:53.900 --> 00:12:57.600
Hey. look.
its lasers light up. Take that. Zurg!

212
00:12:57.500 --> 00:13:00.300
Quick. make a space.
This is where the spaceship lands.

213
00:13:00.400 --> 00:13:03.400
And he does it like that.
And he does a karate chop action!

214
00:13:03.500 --> 00:13:06.400
Come on down. guys!
It's time for games!

215
00:13:19.900 --> 00:13:21.800
- What is it?
- Can you see it?

216
00:13:21.800 --> 00:13:25.400
- What the heck is up there?
- Woody. who's up there with ya?

217
00:13:25.300 --> 00:13:27.400
- Woody?

218
00:13:27.400 --> 00:13:30.800
- What are you doing under the bed?
- Uh. nothin'. Uh. nothin'.

219
00:13:30.800 --> 00:13:33.500
I'm sure Andy was just
a little excited. that's all.

220
00:13:33.600 --> 00:13:36.000
Too much cake and ice cream.
I suppose. It's just a mistake!

221
00:13:36.100 --> 00:13:39.800
Well. that mistake is sitting
in your spot. Woody.

222
00:13:39.700 --> 00:13:42.900
Have you been replaced? -
What did I tell you earlier?

223
00:13:42.900 --> 00:13:45.300
No one is getting replaced

224
00:13:45.300 --> 00:13:48.500
Now. let's all be polite and give
whatever it is up there...

225
00:13:48.400 --> 00:13:52.000
a nice. big
Andy's-room welcome.

226
00:14:15.600 --> 00:14:17.800
- Buzz Lightyear to Star Command.

227
00:14:17.800 --> 00:14:20.200
Come in. Star Command.

