00:14:20.200 --> 00:14:22.500
- Star Command. come
in. Do you read me?

229
00:14:22.500 --> 00:14:26.100
Why don't they answer?
My ship!

230
00:14:28.600 --> 00:14:31.900
Blast! This'll take
weeks to repair.

231
00:14:31.900 --> 00:14:34.900
Buzz Lightyear mission log.
stardate 4-0-7-2.

232
00:14:34.800 --> 00:14:38.100
My ship has run off course
en route to sector 12.

233
00:14:38.200 --> 00:14:40.600
I've crash-landed
on a strange planet.

234
00:14:40.700 --> 00:14:43.100
The impact must've awoken me
from hypersleep.

235
00:14:44.800 --> 00:14:47.600
Terrain seems
a bit unstable.

236
00:14:47.600 --> 00:14:50.900
No readout yet
if the air is breathable.

237
00:14:50.900 --> 00:14:53.300
And there seems to be no sign
of intelligent life anywhere.

238
00:14:53.300 --> 00:14:55.200
- Hello!

239
00:14:55.200 --> 00:14:57.700
Whoa! H-Hey!
Whoa. whoa. whoa. whoa. whoa!

240
00:14:57.700 --> 00:15:00.200
- Did I frighten you? Didn't mean to.

241
00:15:00.200 --> 00:15:02.700
- Sorry. Howdy. My name is Woody.

242
00:15:02.700 --> 00:15:06.900
And this is Andy's room.
That's all I wanted to say.

243
00:15:06.800 --> 00:15:09.200
And also. there has been
a bit of a mix-up.

244
00:15:09.200 --> 00:15:11.500
This is my spot. see.
the bed here.

245
00:15:11.500 --> 00:15:14.000
Local law enforcement.
It's about time you got here.

246
00:15:14.000 --> 00:15:16.900
I'm Buzz Lightyear. Space Ranger.
Universe Protection Unit.

247
00:15:16.900 --> 00:15:19.400
My ship has crash-landed
here by mistake.

248
00:15:19.300 --> 00:15:22.600
Yes. it is a mistake because.
you see. the bed here is my spot.

249
00:15:22.600 --> 00:15:24.900
I need to repair
my turbo boosters.

250
00:15:24.900 --> 00:15:27.400
Do you people still use fossil fuel. or
have you discovered crystallic fusion?

251
00:15:27.400 --> 00:15:30.100
- Well. let's see. We got double-A's.

252
00:15:30.100 --> 00:15:31.700
Watch yourself!
Halt! Who goes there?

253
00:15:31.700 --> 00:15:33.900
Don't shoot!
It's okay. Friends.

254
00:15:33.900 --> 00:15:37.800
