415
00:25:07.200 --> 00:25:09.800
"Don't count on it"?

416
00:25:23.000 --> 00:25:25.000
Mmm!

417
00:25:29.100 --> 00:25:31.400
Buzz! Oh. Buzz!
Buzz Lightyear.

418
00:25:31.400 --> 00:25:34.100
Buzz Lightyear.
thank goodness. We've got trouble!

